_sText:
Okay when i first started surf_ag_constrats it was in dev textures and i continued that theme into the v2 but then i realized that dev textures are kinda plain so i change it up a little and now the textures (not all the same i might add) actually fit the name of the map!

*Added Stuff/Fix*

* The ramps are the same
* I added a credit box with a custom decal so i need to know if that works i used ratpak and there are NO VIRUS'
* More ramps
* more secrets
* Added "spotlights" to make it better
* The glass out side of jail is now thinner
* The second AWP point right above jail has a bigger tele to top so u wont die if you fall off.

Thats about it for the redux version of surf_ag_constrast 

Hope you enjoy my map!
